OL,3,CGrand National's only female winner
OL,4,Cinducted as a legend at Aintree
OL,6,FRachael Blackmore - the only woman to
OL,7,Fwin the Grand National - has been
OL,8,Finducted as a legend, on the opening
OL,9,Fday of the races at Aintree.
OL,11,FBlackmore, 36, who won the
OL,12,Fsteeplechase in 2021 on Minella Times,
OL,13,Fwas presented the plaque as she
OL,14,Funveiled the racecourse's new alcohol-
OL,15,Ffree space "Blackmore's".
OL,17,FHer legends plaque will be displayed
OL,18,Fon the wall of the space, alongside
OL,19,Fartwork by street art specialists
OL,20,FMurWalls and local children from Holy
OL,21,FRosary School in Aintree.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
