OL,3,CGrand National's only female winner
OL,4,Cinducted as a legend at Aintree
OL,6,FWho is Rachael Blackmore?
OL,8,FRachael Blackmore is an Irish jockey
OL,9,Fwho became the first woman to win the
OL,10,FGrand National, when she rode Minella
OL,11,FTimes in the steeplechase in 2021.
OL,13,FShe is also the first woman to ride
OL,14,Fthe winner of a championship race at
OL,15,Fthe Cheltenham Festival just weeks
OL,16,Fbefore her landmark victory at Aintree.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775811900
OL,3,CGrand National's only female winner
OL,4,Cinducted as a legend at Aintree
OL,6,FBlackmore retired in May 2025, with a
OL,7,Ftotal of 575 career wins, and joins
OL,8,Flegends of the sport Ginger McCain,
OL,9,FJenny Pitman and JP McManus to be
OL,10,Fnamed a Grand National Legend.
OL,12,FBlackmore said: "Aintree is just such
OL,13,Fan incredibly special place and I was
OL,14,Fso lucky to have an amazing day here
OL,15,Fin 2021, and I absolutely love coming
OL,16,Fback here.
OL,18,F"I love Liverpool - I love the city, I
OL,19,Flove the people, and it's just a
OL,20,Ffantastic place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775811901
OL,3,CGrand National's only female winner
OL,4,Cinducted as a legend at Aintree
OL,6,F"When I see the list of names -
OL,7,Fincluding equine athletes - on the
OL,8,FGrand National Legends roll of honour,
OL,9,Fit's so special to be part of that and
OL,10,Fa great honour.
OL,12,F"And to see this beautiful bar opened
OL,13,F- I never thought there'd be a
OL,14,Fracecourse bar named after me! It's a
OL,15,Fvery special thing. It does hit home
OL,16,Fhow lucky I am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775811901
OL,3,CGrand National's only female winner
OL,4,Cinducted as a legend at Aintree
OL,6,F"I think it is a brilliant initiative
OL,7,Fto have an alcohol-free space; it's a
OL,8,Freally cool place, there's something
OL,9,Felse on offer. I don't drink myself,
OL,10,Fso I'd better be able to get a free
OL,11,Fhot chocolate in a minute!"
OL,13,FAintree Racecourse Chair Julian Taylor
OL,14,Fsaid: "It is an enormous privilege for
OL,15,Fus to be able to induct you as an
OL,16,FAintree Legend. Your great moment here
OL,17,Fin 2021 was one that none of us will
OL,18,Fever forget.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
