PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775811901
OL,3,CGrand National's only female winner
OL,4,Cinducted as a legend at Aintree
OL,6,F"You are a sporting icon, not just
OL,7,Fhere at Aintree but globally, and you
OL,8,Fare also a lovely human being. Many
OL,9,Fcongratulations to you."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
